CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Flash Newspicture Magazine, January 17, 1938, pg. unknown, reads: "'Charming Matrons and Petite Maids all, the ever-ready camera-man presents this photo of the membership of the most exclusive of all the social clubs in Pgh., the Matron's and Maid's. (Photos by Cameraman Chas. 'Teenie' Harris)."
TitMainTitle: Woman wearing two piece costume dancing in front of band with bass drum inscribed "...night owls...," and audience, including Charlotte Enty Catlin holding small light colored purse, in Loendi Club
